RTI International last week hosted the 2016 symposium on non-communical diseases in Nairobi, in conjunction with the Ministry of Health and NCD Alliance Kenya.Held at the Safari Park Hotel, the event brought together local, regional and international health researchers and stakeholders to provide an opportunity to share ongoing research, identify research needs and formulate a coordinated road map on the issue.The symposium came to a close with the hosts putting together a cocktail party at the same venue.